{"tid":1707012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勢要令11.11成為支那禁語","createTime":"2019-11-11T08:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T05:15:18.000Z","uid":54832,"like":91,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"93981532571400a3f544ca8c86b7f51c87097169","tid":1707012,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:14:11.000Z","msg":"當班大陸人同港豬係雙十一不斷買垃圾既同時，香港人無係呢一日付出左慘痛既代價。<br />\n<br />\n法治已死，無論基層點反抗，上面仲係有一班為利是圖既高層係度泯滅良心，為錢出賣香港人。<br />\n<br />\n所謂雙十一光棍節瘋狂勁減，創造單日幾多億銷售額都好，我地要雙十一呢一日成為支那既禁語，從此只有11月11日黑警濫殺無辜，再無所謂既光棍節。"},{"pid":"44983e876c77b6af6be8e648abd2093579726fc6","tid":1707012,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:16:32.000Z","msg":"啱 有諗頭"},{"pid":"438c910caf8527b14c9313d07d92db6049f1c947","tid":1707012,"uid":54832,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"要係經濟上同支那攬炒<br />\n等雙11呢個字永遠都唔可以<br />\n用來做銷售宣傳字眼"},{"pid":"31d4e0e1d94620655a53f54a6cf356bb12f0a7ff","tid":1707012,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:24:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3bcf5929f446321e0dfaca058bf20b023848ebb","tid":1707012,"uid":235277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:25:41.000Z","msg":"yeah 8964.1111"},{"pid":"754805d9ef83619c5f9c3b0fcad9634e18c8e48a","tid":1707012,"uid":281960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:25:43.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"36fc3fe048a2645c033168dc43c982ea2a13b71d","tid":1707012,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:29:52.000Z","msg":"騎劫返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f69b7bca1e1fdcbea6ba67ee7773f84276ae0e0","tid":1707012,"uid":54832,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"根據新京報網報導，11月11日0時，天貓全球狂歡節開幕，成交額超過100億元人民幣僅用了96秒，比2018年少了29秒。到0時12分49秒，天 貓成交額就突破了500億。天貓的1000億交易額大關則是在1小時03分59秒突破，比去年快了43分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n相信香港人都唔想睇到呢d情況出現，<br />\n勢要同雙11攪攬炒"},{"pid":"0c0450e94ac57204848f842495da8a677596b4d4","tid":1707012,"uid":54832,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:43:47.000Z","msg":"雙11 = 香港版64"},{"pid":"a971ef7284529053d18ea6dafeae3d3384237d4d","tid":1707012,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e9ea7825012e2d87216a7ca59c72a098563bef","tid":1707012,"uid":20262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:47:23.000Z","msg":"淘寶開槍射殺"},{"pid":"66a9de3f06785c44850a04a51cac57257f857791","tid":1707012,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:49:04.000Z","msg":"雙11 = 香港版64"},{"pid":"83e50350645e7374b4b145b7568ba1e063eca48c","tid":1707012,"uid":261773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"11.11<br />\n= 四支槍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0850462f70bdd6b64b9e5a340f81891fde99895","tid":1707012,"uid":213415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:50:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ab55266e16a795b768081e0755f7330b23b5641","tid":1707012,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:55:27.000Z","msg":"雙11 香港黑警無差別徒殺市民"},{"pid":"78cfadda34ab965529cd540a921a298a177f09f4","tid":1707012,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:08:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"439f9a4fabc137389023f5c24cc3851a24d6d0de","tid":1707012,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:32:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6231d39d45c2a723da7c76ef00b33e23d074eabc","tid":1707012,"uid":25794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"1111同CHINA"},{"pid":"8cd394ab02